      "props": {
        "content": "Anthropic offers model → SDK → Managed Agents. Google offers model → ADK → Vertex Agent Engine. OpenAI offers model → Codex (cloud-only). graph-os offers ANY model → Lev (local-first) → graph-os.ai (cloud) + federated mesh (no one else has this)."
      }
